            <title>[CASSANDRA-199] Row.columnFamilies_ is initialized to Hashtable in one place, HashMap in another</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-199</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;which is right?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;note that this behavior dates to the initial import into apache svn.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12426393">CASSANDRA-199</key>
